title: Air Fryer Easy Low - Calorie Blooming Onion
description:
Air Frying a easy low calorie Blooming Onion at 370 to 400 degrees for about 25 to 30 minutes, depending on how hot your particluar air fryer gets.
I used Don's Chuck Wagon All purpose seasoned Onion Ring Mix
Oil Sprayer is Cook's Companion https://evine.com
